description:
Barely surviving her battle with a robotic ninja, airhead assassin Bunny is rescued by Ao-Lung, Dragon of the South Wind, and his star pupil, Kyoto. In return for their kindness (and a big, shiny reward), all she needs to do is retrieve a powerful artifact and have it destroyed. No problem -- if she can stop tripping on her undone bootlaces.

Note: The digital edition (7/13/2016) for this issue was released before the print edition.

“This is our battleground.” The scientists at Comtech discover the truth behind Hotel’s sudden arrival, and their crucial mission. A never ending war wages in the distant future, and its outcome depends on their success. But can the Chief be trusted? And who’s really in Charge?
name: Chapter 02

description:
Sergeant Bill Marsh seemed to bear a charmed life - or so his men said. Time after time he missed death by a hair's breadth. What his men didn't know was that Bill had been told by an African witch-doctor that he would be killed by a lion - and there weren't any lions in France.

Or were there? Nobody could foresee the monster which Bill would soon have to face.
name: Mark of the Lion

description:
Strange things happen in the African desert - especially in the "Region of Devils". But these three lost L.R.D.G. soldiers had never seen anything as weird as this... being helped in their desperate mission by Persian soldiers straight from the pages of history 2000 years ago.

"Prof", Jack and Duncan didn't know whether to be glad - or just plain terrified!
name: The Lost Army

description:
Pete Owen was a fine pilot in a Mosquito night-fighter squadron, with a growing number of kills to his name.

Then he shook everybody by flying his plane, complete with the latest top-secret radar, across the Channel into German hands. He'd been playing a traitor's game all the time, it seemed.

But why was he now in a German prison camp? And why was he spending every minute planning an escape? All he'd get in Britain would be a firing squad.
name: Night Intruder

description:
The order was simple - "Kill Mackheim". The reason was also simple - he was a masterful German general who could thwart the Allied advance in this region of Italy.

Captain Harry Brown, a skilled assassin, was already in the area, operating with the partisans. He was the obvious choice for the job, but there was one snag - he had lost the will to kill in cold blood...
name: Reluctant Assassin

description: As the Battle of Berlin erupts on land, we take a breath underwater in Atlantis to witness who, between Mera and Hila, becomes the rightful heir of her queendom undersea.
name: Chapter 52

description:
A war is coming and, once again, Humans and Elves have to join forces for their survival... Thanks to the sacrifices of Princess Llali and Yfass the wood elf, Humans and Elves have repelled the Orcs and saved the city of Eysine.

However, the future appears very dark for the men of Eysine and their Elven allies, as thousands of Nordrënn ships are swarming their coasts.

Unless the Elf Queen finds the Green Crystal in time, they are all doomed.
name: The Crystal of the Wood Elves

description:
In an effort to save Sarah, her friends must attack haunted London. But they are going to have to face a combined ghost and human army unlike any they've ever faced.

Note: The digital edition (7/13/2016) for this issue was released before the print edition.
Get your first look into the Marvel Universe after CIVIL WAR II! You'll be shocked and amazed at what's coming up this fall in MARVEL NOW!

Supernatural bounty hunter John Tower has long been a man shrouded in mystery. Now, discover what set him on this path of horror as his origins are finally uncovered, revealing just what Tower is risking his life to find!

With the final puzzle piece of his quest in the grasp of The Brotherhood of the Rose, Tower enlists the help of a savage old foe for an all-out assault. Will the threat of a common enemy protect him from the danger by his side?

As the Burning Legion advances across the land, tauren chieftains gather for a momentous summit. An ancient artifact, the mystic Hammer of Khaz’goroth, may hold the power to protect their territory, but will its magic corrupt all who touch it?
name: Highmountain: A Mountain Divided

description:
The Immortal Brijit sends her newest Enforcer to retrieve Melanie. Valin tries to fend off the attack, but how can a powerless human, however well-trained, hope to defeat an undead creature imbued with demonic powers?

2166, THE ERA OF THE APOCALYPSE ENTERS ITS FINAL PHASE - THE LAST TIMES.

In a world dominated by religious zeal and politics, in the New Jerusalem that has become the center of the world, a destructive God has been created by a group of religious fanatics.

Yiu, a mercenary killer paid by the clergy, having completed her last mission by eliminating Shu Fat, is about to undertake her next - to hunt and eliminate the nascent God.
name: Pray That She Dies
